WEBVTT

00:06.632 --> 00:09.635
- [wind whistling]
- [engine running]

00:15.390 --> 00:17.460
MAN ON RADIO: <i>...law enforcement
officials across the state,</i>

00:17.485 --> 00:19.132
<i>but with dangerously low temperatures,</i>

00:19.157 --> 00:21.148
<i>the search for 11-year-old Henry Deaver</i>

00:21.173 --> 00:23.382
<i>has been called off
until the spring thaw,</i>

00:23.407 --> 00:26.338
<i>in what's now considered
a recovery, not a rescue.</i>

00:26.363 --> 00:27.989
<i>Meteorologists say the last time</i>

00:28.014 --> 00:29.806
<i>low temperatures broke minus-thirty...</i>

00:29.831 --> 00:32.815
[Gene Pitney] <i>♪ Dearest darlin' ♪</i>

00:32.840 --> 00:37.978
<i>♪ I had to write to say that
I won't be home anymore ♪</i>

00:37.979 --> 00:41.827
<i>♪ 'Cause something happened to me ♪</i>

00:41.852 --> 00:43.725
<i>♪ While I was driving home ♪</i>

00:43.750 --> 00:46.845
<i>♪ And I'm not the same anymore ♪</i>

00:46.870 --> 00:49.455
<i>♪ Oh, I was only ♪</i>

00:49.480 --> 00:53.696
<i>♪ 24 hours from Tulsa ♪</i>

00:53.721 --> 00:55.473
[open-door alarm buzzing]

