<i>♪♪</i>

01:47.882 --> 01:49.425
[thud]

01:51.135 --> 01:52.470
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

02:01.645 --> 02:03.898
[huffing]

02:11.572 --> 02:13.074
[sighs]

02:38.182 --> 02:39.517
[shivers]

02:54.115 --> 02:57.451
[creaking]

03:04.083 --> 03:06.127
[eerie howling-like sound]

03:18.992 --> 03:20.893
MAN: Henry?

03:22.463 --> 03:24.548
Henry!

03:26.503 --> 03:27.963
Henry!

03:32.478 --> 03:37.437
<font color="#0080ff">Synced & corrected by</font> kinglouisxx
